  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winna tappê dohta\nWaldischana/ un Gohdiba/ un\nta Walstiba/ ka wiſſeein Laudim/\nTautahm un Wallo dahm to bij\ngohdaht/ winna Waldischana\nirr weena muhschiga Waldischa-\nna/ kas ne iſnihēs/ un winna\nWalstiba ne tapē famattata.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Man Dantjelam nogurre\nmannâ Sirđē eekſch mannahm\nMeesahm/ un tahē Parahdischa-\nnas iſtruhztinaja manni/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es peegahju pee weena\nno teem/ kas tur stahweja / un\nwaizaju no ta to Paterfibu pahr\nto wiſfu. Un winch iſteize man\nto/ un iſtahstiia man tahē pa-\nſchas Leetas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee tschetri leeli Swehri\nirr tschetri Kehnini/ kas no tahē\nSemmes zelſees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet ta Wiſfu-augstaka\nSwehtee eedabbuhs to Walstibu/\nun turrehs to muhschigi/ir muh-\nschtgi muhscham.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pehz gribbeju es to Pa-\nteesibu finnaht no ta zettorta\nSwehra/ kam zittahds Gihmis\nbija ne ka wiſſeem zitteem/ fehti\nbreesungs/ ka Sobbi no Dſelsee\nbija/ un winna Naggi no War-\nra/ tas ehde un fatreeze/ un fa-\nwinne to zittu ar fawahm Rah-\njahin.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no winna deſinite\nRaggeim/ kas us winna Gal-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es redſeju to patchu Ra-\ngu karrojam prett teem Swe-\nteem/ un arri tahē pahrwarra-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Teekans tas Wezz-\natnahze/ un ta Wiſfu-augst\nSwehteem to Teefu nefte/un\ntas nospreests Laiks atnahze/\nteem Swehteem bij to Wal-\nbu eedabhuht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wisch fazztja ta: De-\nzettorts Swehrs buhs ta zett\nta Walstiba wirs Semmes/\nzittada buhs neka wiſſas zit\nWalstibas/ un tahē ehdihe ni-\nfu Semmi / un famihs un\ntreeks to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee definitē Raggt\ntadeht: No tahē Walstibas\nfees definitē Kehnini/ un we-\nzittaig pehz teem zelſees/ un\nbuhs jo warrens neka tee pir-\njee / un pasemmohs trihs �-\nninus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas runnahē Wa-\ndus prett to Wiſfu-augst-\nSwehtus/ un aprentjees La-\nun Banfibu pahrgrebsibt /\ntee taps winnam Rohkā dol-\nweenu Laiku/ un kahdusLaik-\nun puts Laiku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz to taps ta T-\n"
    }
  ],
